replies.body:
I'm disappointed that champions with a mask don't get a Blood Moon skin, like {{champion:203}} I mean okay you want yet another rushed Katarina {{champion:55}}  skin for her mains to complain about, and another forced Yi {{champion:11}} skin that I think Yi mains will despise, but did Tryndamere really need this scuffed Warring Kingdoms chroma?

We could have had [Blood Moon Kayn](https://pm1.narvii.com/6688/452a53caa1f91c50f23265ad3ec63058dec63481_hq.jpg) {{champion:141}} or [Blood Moon Syndra](https://us.v-cdn.net/5021068/uploads/editor/rk/hhak7x6bhi78.jpg) {{champion:134}} 

But the skin development team is really performing poorly lately and giving us rushed skins with no soul put into them.
